,"tag-supplication-al-dua","tag-surah-al-tawbah","tag-virtue-al-fadail","tag-wealth-al-mal","tag-women-al-nisa"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-6vZ","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":19373,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/20\/honor-nobility-taqwa\/","url_meta":{"origin":25047,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Honor: Nobility is in the fear of Allah, al-Taqwa","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 20, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Samurah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHonor itself is wealth, and nobility is in the fear of Allah.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3271 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u064e\u0645\u064f\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0628\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0643\u064e\u0631\u064e\u0645\u064f \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0651\u064e\u0642\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0649 3271 \u0633\u0646\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0631\u0645\u0630\u064a \u0643\u062a\u0627\u0628\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5171,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/15\/trial-of-ummah-wealth\/","url_meta":{"origin":25047,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Wealth: Trial of the M